title: JUNGLER FOR 5'S TEAM
body:
We are a fun group of players that are looking for a jungler to finish off our team so we can start to climb.
Our team consists of an average rank of gold. I am the lowest at silver and highest at diamond. We need a jungler who is happy to play the engage champions but there always room for the odd assassin.

add me in game, snugglemuffin and leave a comment on this chat. We can do some trial games to see if you like me and the same back

Must have Skype, Hope to hear from you :D

replies.body: If you wanted to get in on the jungle spot still ill b running a few games with the people that are interested 7pm Monday night. that is going by Victorian time so if its different google it :D. if you are keen try to hop online and add me. IGN : snugglemuffin
AA Warmachine, have alot of xp in s5 jungle , will play any champ, sometimes even try to brake the meta in solo q.
ZoharMasni Gold 2 nice to meet u guys

I can play decent engage champions been jungling sense season 2, have a decent understanding of fight/flight and when to push certain objectives..
Only problem is i work in the afternoons and don't normally finish until 6:30 GMT+8 but am available any time after that every night..
Will send an add, hope to hear from you and maybe play some games :)

Friend Request sent, currently Gold 3.
Jungle main have been playing since beta.
